/ET_Cetera/Akshay_dedicates_Padmashri_to_fans/articleshow/4032826.cms|title=Overwhelmed Akshay Kumar dedicates Padmashri to fans|date=26 January 2009|work=[[The Economic Times]]|accessdate=26 January 2009|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130230845/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/ET_Cetera/Akshay_dedicates_Padmashri_to_fans/articleshow/4032826.cms|archivedate=30 January 2009|publisher=[[The Times Group]]|location=India}}</ref> In 2011, [[The Asian Awards]] honoured Kumar for his outstanding achievement in Cinema.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/akshay-kumar-honoured-at-annual-asian-awards/194882-8-66.html|title=Akshay Kumar honoured at Annual Asian awards|accessdate=7 September 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228113223/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/akshay-kumar-honoured-at-annual-asian-awards/194882-8-66.html|archivedate=28 February 2014|publisher=[[CNN-IBN]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/Superstars-who-have-never-won-awards/photostory/30284558.cms|title=Superstars who have never won awards|work=[[The Times of India]]|accessdate=7 September 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417023500/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/Superstars-who-have-never-won-awards/photostory/30284558.cms|archivedate=17 April 2014|publisher=[[The Times Group]]}}</ref>

